    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Manly West.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Manly West?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">School catchments, bayside proximity and the suburb's family-oriented residential character are the primary value drivers in Manly West. The suburb's position adjacent to Manly gives residents practical access to the Cambridge Parade precinct and the Manly Boat Harbour without the premium that a Manly address requires. Homes on well-maintained internal streets within strong school catchments attract consistent competition from committed family buyers in the eastern corridor.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Manly West?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Manly West homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. Family buyers who have identified the eastern bayside corridor as the right location and have done their catchment and suburb research tend to be decisive when the right property appears. Autumn and spring bring the strongest open home activity, but the suburb draws consistent demand from families making a deliberate move east throughout the year.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Manly West?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Manly West offers a relaxed, family-oriented lifestyle in the eastern bayside corridor. The suburb provides the residential space and school access that family buyers seek, with the Manly Cambridge Parade precinct and the Manly Boat Harbour accessible from the suburb's eastern edge. It is a community defined by families who have made a deliberate choice to be part of the bayside corridor.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Manly West a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Manly West offers solid value for families comparing the eastern bayside corridor. The suburb delivers school catchments, good block sizes and proximity to the Manly bayside lifestyle at a more accessible price point than Manly proper. Consistent family buyer demand from people making a deliberate move to the east has supported the market, and the suburb's position as the gateway to the bayside corridor gives it ongoing appeal for long-term owner-occupiers.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

